BLE RGB LED

Control a RGB LED connected to an Arduino with Bluetooth Low Energy, using a RedBearLab BLE Shield.

Arduino Installation

1. unzip libBLEShield_v1.0.zip to <arduinosketchbook>/libraries folder
2. load BleRgbLed sketch into your Arduino

Mac OSX

1. Requires Mac OS X 10.7.2 or later, Xcode 4.2 or later
2. Requires Bluetooth Low Energy capable Mac or BT 4.0 USB Dongle